<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c4">[٨٧٣]</span> أَبُو بُرْدةَ، أَخُو أَبِي مُوسَى <span class="c2">(١)</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>اسْمُهُ عَامِرُ بنُ قَيْسٍ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>ماتَ سَنةَ أَرْبعٍ ومِائةٍ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[٨٧٤]</span> أَبُو إِيَاسٍ البَجَليُّ <span class="c2">(٢)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>اسْمُهُ عَامِرُ بنُ عَبْدةَ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>سَمِعَ ابنَ مَسْعودٍ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>رَوى عنهُ المُسَيَّبُ بنُ رَافعٍ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[٨٧٥]</span> أَبُو جعفر الخَطْمِيُّ <span class="c2">(٣)</span>.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>اسْمُهُ عُمَيرُ بنُ يَزيدَ بنِ عُمَيرِ بنِ حَبِيبِ بنِ خُماشةَ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>قالهُ أَحْمدُ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c4">[٨٧٦]</span> أَبُو المُعَذَّلِ الطُّفاوِيُّ <span class="c2">(٤)</span>.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>اسْمُهُ عَطيّةُ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c4">[٨٧٧]</span> أَبُو هَاشِمٍ الزَّعْفرانيُّ البَصريُّ <span class="c2">(٥)</span>.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>اسْمُهُ عَمّارُ بنُ عُمارةَ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c4">[٨٧٨]</span> أَبُو مَهَلٍ الجُعْفيُّ <span class="c2">(٦)</span>.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>اسْمُهُ عُروةُ بنُ عَبْدِ اللَّهِ بنِ قُشَيرٍ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
